00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:34,640
I pulled the employee list
from the agencies

429
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:36,400
that do maintenance
on Ember Copley's building.

430
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:39,840
Looking for an employee that had
access to both victims' apartments.

431
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:41,800
That's a hell of a lot of people.

