00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:43,520
<i>Yeah, but our guy's been real busy.</i>

433
00:24:44,320 --> 00:24:46,480
He had to have called in sick
the last couple days.

434
00:24:46,560 --> 00:24:47,720
Get Nygma in there.

435
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:49,200
He's freaky good with puzzles.

436
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:50,960
<i>You got it.</i>

437
00:24:53,680 --> 00:24:55,960
- Renee, we have to talk.
- What are you doing here?

438
00:24:56,040 --> 00:24:58,080
Look, I know you think
he's done terrible things,

439
00:24:58,160 --> 00:25:00,360
but I also know you care
about the truth.

440
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:02,240
You shouldn't be here.
Barbara, you shouldn't be seen here.

441
00:25:02,320 --> 00:25:03,880
Damn it, Renee,
will you listen to me?

442
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:06,800
Look, I'll work with you, okay?

443
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:09,760
I will tell you whatever I know,
whatever I can find out.

444
00:25:09,840 --> 00:25:12,600
I need you to keep an open mind,
okay?

445
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:13,800
It's too late for that.

446
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:16,480
Whatever's happening,
you've got it wrong, Renee.

447
00:25:16,560 --> 00:25:19,080
He can't tell me, I know that,
but it isn't what you think.

448
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:20,840
He's trying to protect me.

449
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:23,280
He won't tell me who's out there,
who he's afraid of.

450
00:25:23,360 --> 00:25:24,840
He's right not to.

451
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:27,160
- Wait, why?
- Because it'll get you killed.

452
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:28,920
Okay? You understand?

453
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:32,360
What he knows, who he knows,
will kill you.

454
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:37,680
We got a judge issuing
a warrant tonight.

455
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:40,840
Barbara, you know how much
I care about you.

456
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:43,280
When Gordon gets arrested,
you have to get out of here.

457
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,280
If Jim gets arrested,

458
00:25:45,360 --> 00:25:48,120
then this is exactly
where I have to be, by his side.

459
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:50,000
Please, just leave.

460
00:25:50,080 --> 00:25:52,120
Get out of Gotham
just till this is over.

461
00:25:53,080 --> 00:25:54,160
And don't come to me again.

462
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:04,080
Okay, so four guys have called
in sick since last week.

463
00:26:04,160 --> 00:26:06,040
The two suspects from
the outer boroughs are cleared,

464
00:26:06,120 --> 00:26:07,600
another is out of state,

465
00:26:07,680 --> 00:26:09,760
but apparently,
it's unconfirmed, so...

466
00:26:09,840 --> 00:26:13,360
- So that leaves one last guy.
- Raymond Earl.

467
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:17,000
Shift supervisor says
he's been squatting in a place,

468
00:26:17,080 --> 00:26:19,120
near Cannery Park somewhere
around the 1100 block.

469
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:20,600
- That's him.
- You sure?

470
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:21,760
Yeah, I'm sure.

471
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:23,080
I'm 100 percent sure.

472
00:26:42,720 --> 00:26:43,920
Déjà voodoo all day long.

473
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:48,920
This is where we got Randall Milkie
ten years ago.

474
00:26:50,280 --> 00:26:51,440
This is where Dix fell.

475
00:26:52,840 --> 00:26:53,840
Bullock.

476
00:26:56,440 --> 00:26:58,000
Gotta go in. Come on.

477
00:26:58,080 --> 00:26:59,840
Yeah. Yeah.

478
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:06,720
We're going to put you to sleep
for good now.

479
00:27:07,600 --> 00:27:10,400
You're lucky to be the sacrifice.

480
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:50,960
Go get her.

481
00:28:02,600 --> 00:28:04,440
It's okay. You're safe.

482
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:09,560
You all right?

483
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:11,160
Okay.

484
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:37,280
You'll never stop the Goat.

485
00:28:39,800 --> 00:28:43,000
- I will always come back.
- Quit saying that.

486
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:12,880
Raymond Earl, you're under arrest.

487
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:16,200
Not bad.

488
00:29:19,040 --> 00:29:20,040
All right.

489
00:29:22,760 --> 00:29:23,760
All right.

