00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:20,040
I'm worried for you.

494
00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:23,080
So anxious you look.

495
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:29,720
These moves you make,
they're safe, yes?

496
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:34,280
- You're not doing anything illegal?
