00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:53,640
But you know what?

502
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:56,760
I think I finally found somebody
I can trust.

503
00:31:58,600 --> 00:32:01,080
- A policeman.
- Police?

504
00:32:01,960 --> 00:32:05,080
- The police are liars.
